sterling_stingray = Product.create(name: "Sterling by Music Man StingRay Ray4 Electric Bass Satin Transparent Black Black Pickguard", used: false, price: 229.99, description: "The StingRay Ray4 electric bass is the cousin of the Music Man StingRay 4 bass. Classic, iconic instruments that defined a generation of bassists since the late '70s. Active electronics, low-noise hum bucking pickups, rock-solid hardware and a simple, uncluttered look that is instantly recognizable and respected.
